{"tid":880683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞羞辱皇馬一幕重現！魯營亮五指山嘲諷皇馬","createTime":"2018-10-29T01:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T02:47:44.000Z","uid":147522,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"05e897b2b3f6691c7f23a2b63752d3867b0072dd","tid":880683,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T01:41:33.000Z","msg":"　　<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/29/094126_1b26949fbda506028f7f795656b1ee89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2F094126_1b26949fbda506028f7f795656b1ee89.png&h=0ec04f71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/29/094131_7e067d96dd36601d92b8afcfb0251add.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2F094131_7e067d96dd36601d92b8afcfb0251add.png&h=4815b3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n        5-1！巴塞面對皇馬又製造了大比數慘案，在作客吞下5粒失球，讓皇馬想起了不美好的回憶。而魯營的球迷也不會錯過羞辱皇馬的機會。<br />\n<br />\n　　上半場巴塞就取得了2-0的優勢，雖然下半場皇馬一度有所起色，並且由馬些路扳回一球，但後半段他們徹底崩潰。拉莫斯也出現了低級失誤，讓蘇亞雷斯完成了帽子戲法。最終，兩位後備出場的球員迪比利和維達爾攜手殺死了比賽，比數最終定格在了5-1。<br />\n<br />\n　　對於這個比數，巴塞球迷十分滿意。在維達爾入球之後，魯營的球迷興奮異常，他們紛紛舉起了自己的雙手，將巴掌亮給了鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n　　這個舉動的含義很明顯，就是諷刺皇馬：你們又被我們進了5球。對陣皇馬攻入5球，讓球迷們想起了2010-11賽季，巴塞主場5-0痛宰皇馬的那場比賽。當時比基就亮出了「五指山」對皇馬進行了嘲諷。而這一幕又在今季的魯營重現了。"},{"pid":"f5b43135aa0227b978344925184fca9dd7391ba9","tid":880683,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146253f95718c2aa1b29d892fd44373686a90f7e","tid":880683,"uid":19527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:15:03.000Z","msg":"🖐🏾"},{"pid":"d59ce101949cb1811639c2e7c13c19f8a41e63c2","tid":880683,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a1d1b8cee79f5f6e0420b067c339faf096787a","tid":880683,"uid":6026,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:19:07.000Z","msg":"今日著件巴塞出街 成街人都望住我又同我揮手👋"},{"pid":"7f6fb067ce86ceec29d480048d5645ac42a0dcee","tid":880683,"uid":68620,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"證明左皇馬咁多年來真係靠c朗一個<br />\n一定成隊散曬，頭6名都無<br />\n等睇降班"},{"pid":"05689c51477aabb7e0f3389bf0d529bcec1fef8d","tid":880683,"uid":123014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f6fb067ce86ceec29d480048d5645ac42a0dcee","tid":880683,"uid":68620,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"證明左皇馬咁多年來真係靠c朗一個<br />\n一定成隊散曬，頭6名都無<br />\n等睇降班"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"我皇既強大 只係因為他朗既光芒照耀住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea901d6a6ff591f063e77d51c669a8ead29fd40d","tid":880683,"uid":144466,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/29/102644_5acc5e39a8153a4b7114a3ecc2ac9ca8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2F102644_5acc5e39a8153a4b7114a3ecc2ac9ca8.jpg&h=5f9f9ccf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f986179555fe494a080bd6f6a5048bc9a3b65644","tid":880683,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"C朗初離隊時，拉莫斯豪言無C朗我們更團結！攻力比前更利害，結果呢⋯⋯"},{"pid":"18f0f99bf8245cfcefe60ffa2dc65b19ce05f392","tid":880683,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.euroresidentes.com/euroresiuk/news-spain/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/10/a4.jpg\" dat